</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p>"Fiat currency is credit, gold is money."<br />And silver is money,<br />and U.S. Notes are money (even though they are "fiat"...)</p>
<p>Money is any accepted purchasing media that has <strong>no interest owed on it</strong>.</p>
<p>Various forms of real money can have vastly different values but they are still money.</p>

